				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, I can think of reasons why it would have been different.  Thanks for the response though <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
I read somewhere else that a suspended pet regens HP.  I just bought Suspend level 1 yesterday, and I suspended epic pet.  He was suspended for around 10 min, when I brought him back out his HP was exactly the same.  So perhaps with suspend level 2 pets do regen, but I don't think they do with level 1.
<br />

<br />
One really neat discovery I made was the pet <span style="font-weight: bold">sends me a tell when I suspend him, and un-suspend him</span>.  That was a pleasant suprise because I have never received a tell from a pet before.  I tried to respond, but it didn't let me.  He says something like "as you wish master" when you suspend him, and something like "I live again" when you bring him back out.
<br />

<br />
Super ability.  Loads of fun.  Makes canni godly.<br />_________________<br /><Center><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=36994" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Eandori Raintree</a></b>
