</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">When the pet has buffs, charm or dots on him and he is suspended, will the spells continue to count duration? If i get backup pet virtued, suspend him and then 2 hours later unsupend, will he still have virtue? Same goes for dots?</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
