				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Might have missed it somewhere, maybe proveiously mentionned, but Suspend Minion II, supposed to restore your pet at the exact state it was before having been suspended, does change two things : 
<br />

<br />
1. Pet Size.
<br />
I always always shrink my pets. Once unsuspended, they recover their full size
<br />

<br />
2. /pet taunt
<br />
I usually set pet taunt off. Once unsuspended, they are back in "taunt ON".
<br />

<br />
No major inconvenience but I would like them corrected.<br />_________________<br />Sage <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381021" target="_blank" class="postlink">Majax Seplu`Komavan</a>
