				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">One easy-to-hope-for thing about Suspend Minion is that it <span style="font-style: italic">switches </span>pets for you. At this time, this is not true. If you attempt to suspend a pet with one already suspended, the ability will fail. I am not aware of any UI indicator or other obvious method of determining if you already have a pet suspended.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=568700" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
