			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Another thing to be aware of is illusion spells such as Night's Dark Terror.
<br />
If the spell has been cast on a pet and that pet is then suspended and unsuspended it will return to it's original form. However the effects of the illusion will still be in effect. The buff icon will still be displayed in the pet's buff window and the /pet report will still list the illusion.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
