				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I hope to start saving AAs for this soon so I want to be clear on the capabilities.
<br />

<br />
In an event such as the HP cycle in CoD, rather than killing my pet before we engage the Mob that spawns a number of skel adds for each player (and pet) death (or feign deaths, or sit downs), I would be able to suspend my pet until that fight is over.  In that case, my pet is not an issue because it is not there.
<br />

<br />
It is typical that one or more players will die in the fight, and others will die because of the adds.  If I am killed, my bind point is in PoTranquility.
<br />

<br />
When I am rezzed back into CoD, will my pet still be suspended because my corpse was still in the zone?  Or will it poof because the real me zoned back to my bind point?<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=528216 newwindow" target="_blank" class="postlink">Canneto Dibari</a>
<br />
65 High Elf Arch Convoker of Fennin Ro</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
